verbose_text: Cells were cultured at a concentration of 2x10 6 cells/mL in 200 muL in 96 wells plate with RPMI 1640 (Invitrogen) supplemented with 10% (v/v) heat inactivated fetal calf serum (FCS), 100 units/mL penicillin G (Invitrogen), 10 mug/mL streptomycin (Invitrogen), 1.25 mug/mL fungizone (Invitrogen), 0.01 M HEPES (N-2-hydroxyethylpiperazine-N '-2-ethanesulfonic acid) and 55 muM 2-mercaptoethanol for 72 h at 37 degreesC in a humidified atmosphere containing 5% (v/v) carbon dioxide.
